  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2 style="text-align: left;">Visit Italy this Summer</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">From city breaks to countryside and lake retreats, discover the best of Italy with Inghams. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">We offer a wide range of hotels in Italy, so whether your ideal trip is driving through the Italian countryside or indulging in great food and wine on the shores of sparkling lakes, we can turn your dream escape into a reality.</span></p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f}#Italian Lakes" title="Italy Holidays" data-anchor="#Italian Lakes">Italian Lakes</a></span> | <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f}#Dolomites" title="Italy Holidays" data-anchor="#Dolomites">Dolomites</a></span> | <a data-udi="umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f}#Neopolitan Riviera" title="Italy Holidays" data-anchor="#Neopolitan Riviera"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Neapolitan Riviera</span></a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f}#Sicily" title="Italy Holidays" data-anchor="#Sicily"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sicily</span></a></h3>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><img src="/media/13089084/italy-cinque-terre-838x400.jpg" alt="Italy Cinque Terre" data-udi="umb://media/05f15ab5673b40979f856a58fad5ec83" /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This summer, you could be walking in the footsteps of spectacular ancient Roman ruins, and setting sights on the world’s greatest art masterpieces. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Terracotta roofs and vineyards stretching over luscious green fields could be your summer reality. Not to mention al fresco cafes serving up the best Italian homemade food.</span></p>
<p><strong>Don't miss out on our limited time Italy savings! </strong></p>
<p><strong>Speak to a member of our UK based team on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</span> or book online.</strong></p>
