<p><a name="Italian Lakes"></a></p>
<h2>Italian Lakes</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Discover the beauty of the Italian Lakes and get ready to succumb to the charms of Lake Garda, Lake Como and Lake Maggiore. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Backed by breath-taking artful landscapes, charming fishing villages and medieval castles, these enchanting lakes will leave you spellbound. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">With excellent access to hiking trails and wild swimming spots, there’s plenty to uncover.</span></p>
