<p><a name="Dolomites"></a></p>
<h2>Dolomites</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Get active and explore Italy’s best kept secret. This striking mountain range offers some of the best Alpine thrills in Europe. You’ll find a limitless number of activities including hiking, cycling, mountain biking, climbing, historic tours, farm visits and wine tasting.</span></p>
