<p><a name="Sicily"></a></p>
<h2>Sicily</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Sicily is home to dazzling landscapes and historic treasures - perfect for an adventure back into the past. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Known as the ‘Island of the sun’, Sicily is as rich in natural beauty as it is in culture and delicious food and wine. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">With coastal roads leading to breath-taking viewpoints, whitewashed towns and emerald green hillsides, this Italian paradise has so much to offer.</span></p>
